WEBVTT

00:02:59.603 --> 00:03:04.259
I wasn't supposed to have
fully resourced biology or chemistry labs,

00:03:04.283 --> 00:03:07.085
school buses that brought me door-to-door,

00:03:07.109 --> 00:03:09.537
freshly prepared school lunches

00:03:09.561 --> 00:03:11.305
or even air conditioning.

00:03:12.127 --> 00:03:14.057
These are things my kids don't get.

00:03:14.661 --> 00:03:16.198
You see, as I got older,

00:03:16.222 --> 00:03:19.239
while I was grateful
for this amazing opportunity

00:03:19.263 --> 00:03:20.909
that I was being given,

00:03:20.933 --> 00:03:23.661
there was this ever-present pang of:

00:03:24.210 --> 00:03:26.629
But what about everyone else?

00:03:27.137 --> 00:03:30.507
There are thousands
of other kids just like me,